    "# use .apply()\n",
    "def get_city(address):\n",
    "    return address.split(',')[1]\n",
    "\n",
    "def get_state(address):\n",
    "    return address.split(',')[2].split(' ')[1]\n",
    "\n",
    "all_data['city']=all_data['Purchase Address'].apply(lambda x: f\"{get_city(x)} ({get_state(x)})\")\n",
    "all_data.head()"
   ]
